#define BossBGMEntry(UnitId,SongId) "BYTE UnitId 0 0 0; SHORT SongId 0"
#define BossBGMTerminator "BYTE 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF 0xFF"

ALIGN 4
BossBGMTable:
BossBGMEntry(Skull,BossMusic)
BossBGMEntry(Ch2BeastBoss,BossMusic)
BossBGMEntry(Wise,BossMusic)
BossBGMEntry(Ch4LowlanderBoss,SteelGiantID)
BossBGMEntry(JabberwockBoss,BossMusic)
BossBGMEntry(Muscle,BossMusic)
BossBGMEntry(Recruiter,BossMusic)
BossBGMTerminator

PUSH

ORG $72908
POIN BossBGMTable

POP
